{"type": "article", "id": 30606, "title": "灵感来源于钻石的壁灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-04T22:58:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160804220723kdFnqphQjuwgRsiB.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>          </p><p>当你第一眼看到来自 <a href=\"http://www.andreaclairestudio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Andrea Clair Studio</a> 的 The Diamond 系列时，你或许会惊讶于它简洁而直白的设计：平时它是一件颇大的木制墙面装饰，一旦点亮它就成为了一盏吸睛的壁灯，就像是一颗熠熠生辉的钻石。每一款灯具都在布鲁克林手工打造，木料和内置的金属框架都可以根据用户的喜好进行定制，还可以在镂空处加上一面镜子。如果你有兴趣的话可以通过<a href=\"http://andrea-claire.squarespace.com/diamond-series-1\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>与工作室联系。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804221655Fs5MVQauSvhoXHO0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.633333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804221655wCRXk21BUHWFJN8V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804221656xgRnlA5auSOh9MJF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.416667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804221655odtnJYx9sph4TXmU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}